                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <gloss target="#t_CFM1">CFM</gloss> Files</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">United States Delegation Journal</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-chapter-heading" calendar="gregorian" when="1946-10-05T16:00:00+01:00">October 5, 1946, 4 p.m.</date>
                </dateline>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <gloss target="#t_USDel1">USDel</gloss> (PC) (Journal) 62</p>
                <p>The Reports on the Peace Treaties with Hungary and with Finland were approved in
                    final form with a few minor changes. The final text of the Report on the
                    Bulgarian Treaty will be approved at a morning meeting on October 6.<note n="36" xml:id="d309fn1">The reports under reference are printed in <ref target="frus1946v04">vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">iv</hi>
                        </ref>.</note>
                </p>
